Portrait of the Grand Duchess Maria Feodorovna, 1777. Artist: Alexander Roslin

Portrait of the Grand Duchess Maria Feodorovna, 1777. Detail. Sophie Dorothea of Wurttemberg (1729-1828) was the second wife of Tsar Paul I of Russia, who she married in 1776 when he was still heir to the throne. Found in the collection of The Hermitage, St Petersburg. Heritage Images features heritage image collections. Â© The Art Collector
